Usage: place_cells_at_center_for_feedthrus [-help]
                                           [-insts <list_of_selected_insts>]
                                           [-skipTopInsts]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-insts <list_of_selected_insts>     # To select specific list of unplaced
                                    # instances. Support wildcards.
                                    # (string, optional)
-skipTopInsts                       # Skip placing cells at center for top
                                    # instances (bool, optional)